1.ldesc: A floating mass of |xgrotesque|n tentacles hovers in the void
1.edesc:
A large mass of tentacles is suspended in the void. The large black vine-
shaped tentacles seems to move independently, like they had a mind of their
own. In the center of this misshapen black form lies a gigantic dark-green eye
that stares you at you contently and curiously.
